snippet.title: Here's The Truth About Candace Owens
snippet.description:
In today’s politically-divided country, sometimes the loudest voices are the ones that get talked about most. Turning Point USA Communications Director Candace Owens is undeniably a loud voice, rising to prominence in 2018 as a young Black Trump supporter.

Her YouTube channel features titles that are sure to ruffle feathers, such as “Women Marching In America Again? What a JOKE” and “How to Escape the Democrat Plantation (An Easy Guide).” Owens has also embraced nationalist ideologies, even calling Donald Trump not just “the leader of the free world, but the savior of it as well," continuing, "May God bless America— the last stand for western civilization.” Here’s the untold truth about Candace Owens.
